{"tid":254260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國北斗衛星今年開始全球組網      2020年前形成全球導航能力","createTime":"2017-05-23T05:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T11:37:05.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1c395e148f5429b7223e7468b1eb4d7c8a686e","tid":254260,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/131929_5ef5e2b4995c2e56acf08fda6ed08d24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F131929_5ef5e2b4995c2e56acf08fda6ed08d24.jpg&h=8e7ebb15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017-05-23 11:24<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n在5月23日舉行的第八屆中國衛星導航學術年會開幕式上，中國衛星導航系統委員會主席王力透露，中國計劃今年下半年發射6至8顆全球組網衛星，2018年前後完成18顆衛星發射，率先為&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;沿線國家提供基本服務2020年將建成世界一流的全球衛星導航系統，形成全球導航能力。<br />\n<br />\n北斗系統是中國自主建設，獨立運行的衛星導航系統，為全球用戶提供全天候，全天時，高精度的定位的導航和服務。"},{"pid":"db1d30a9e12d1ca5cbba8681ab15fcd32c57523a","tid":254260,"uid":17022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:23:27.000Z","msg":"哇"},{"pid":"3f7a52412994e5dd4f4bf5daa61ba7c58f6c606c","tid":254260,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"gps 都不用美國"},{"pid":"72b0d2ad5cdfe71571213de7f821cb97218c12cc","tid":254260,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>gps 都不用美國</blockquote><br />\ngps 美國野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc32b2ffddf00a60d8adf75865edc48d071699f","tid":254260,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>gps 都不用美國</blockquote><br />\n&quot;gps&quot; 呢個名就係美國野<br />\n<br />\n俄仔有 GLONASS"},{"pid":"5d121e82551dbe1da15b1db65f12931cfc67b7c6","tid":254260,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blo